00:27:05.080 --> 00:27:08.070
for tax purposes for all
purposes in Kenya now.

00:27:08.070 --> 00:27:11.630
So those group ranches have
become conservation areas

00:27:11.630 --> 00:27:13.120
and won't be broken up.

00:27:13.120 --> 00:27:14.287
And that's really important.

00:27:14.287 --> 00:27:15.745
JOHN BATTELLE: But
they were really

00:27:15.745 --> 00:27:17.465
becoming that well
