And we have got significant
human development

00:35:13.590 --> 00:35:14.450
that is over here.

00:35:14.450 --> 00:35:16.840
And what has happened is that
these two ecosystems have

00:35:16.840 --> 00:35:19.850
been split, or they
had become isolated

00:35:19.850 --> 00:35:21.330
because of development.

00:35:21.330 --> 00:35:23.460
But what happened
in 2009 and 2010

00:35:23.460 --> 00:35:25.540
is that Lewa and other
like-minded partners

00:35:25.540 --> 00:35:30.170
